name: SargeBaldy Speedmapping Compilation #6
description: This is a compilation of the WADs entered in SargeBaldy's sixth speedmapping exercise. Participants were given 100 minutes to create a Doom 2 level on a certain theme. This week's theme was to make a map based on somewhere that you know. This could be your school, your house, your campus, a block of your town, just anywhere that you know well.
